-- Rolta Awarded Memphis Gas, Water Contract for Oracle Project
-- B y   R a n d a l l   H a c k l e y
-- 2013-01-10T12:46:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-10/rolta-awarded-memphis-gas-water-contract-for-oracle-project.html
Rolta International Inc. said it won
a systems and services modernization contract at Memphis Light
Gas & Water for an  Oracle Corp. (ORCL)  e-business project.  The two-year, $31 million contract at the largest three-
service municipal utility in the U.S. includes customizing and
deploying Oracle information technologies to replace a 22-year-
old system and boost efficiencies, the Mumbai-based subsidiary
of  Rolta India Ltd. (RLTA)  said today in a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Randall Hackley in London at 
